Phuak: My kids have fallen asleep
waiting for me.

3007
01:34:35,370 --> 01:34:36,770
Phuak: It's already 3am!

3008
01:34:36,930 --> 01:34:38,080
Oat: Your kid is waiting for you
while sleeping, right?

3009
01:34:38,080 --> 01:34:38,720
Phuak: He fell asleep!

3010
01:34:38,720 --> 01:34:41,900
Oat: At this rate every day, even my dog
won't remember I'm its dad.

3011
01:34:41,900 --> 01:34:43,080
Jeff: Okay okay.

3012
01:34:43,160 --> 01:34:48,880
Running Man Thailand, Never Stop Running!

3013
01:34:50,970 --> 01:34:55,280
PD: Today you will compete in
the "Big Eater Monopoly" mission.

3014
01:34:52,000 --> 01:34:54,760
[This round, the competition
is a foodie version of Monopoly]

3015
01:34:55,280 --> 01:34:56,120
That's it.

3016
01:34:55,380 --> 01:34:58,140
[Get to famous eateries
and reclaim survival privileges]

3017
01:34:56,120 --> 01:34:57,180
Where are we going?

3018
01:34:58,560 --> 01:35:00,400
It's not over yet.

3019
01:34:59,280 --> 01:35:02,840
[A fiery eating battle
with survival privileges at stake]

3020
01:35:02,600 --> 01:35:05,640
Let's go look, I'm starving.

3021
01:35:03,760 --> 01:35:06,200
[Which team will have the last laugh?]
